  "PinObjectiveTip": {
    "English": "<span class=\"name name-earth\">Basalt</span> is found primarily on worlds with a <span class=\"name name-fuel\">volcanic environment</span>. Typically found in large deposits and located with the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Analysis Visor</span>.<br><br>Common ferrite rocks may yield Basalt after inspection with an <span class=\"name name-technology\">Analysis Visor</span>. Basalt may be refined from <span class=\"name name-earth\">Magnetized Ferrite</span> and terrain metals from other <span class=\"name name-fuel\">high-temperature</span> worlds.",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "<span class=\"name name-earth\">玄武岩</span>主要出现在具有<span class=\"name name-fuel\">火山环境</span>的世界里。通常可在大型矿床中找到，可使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>来定位。<br><br>使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>检查常见铁氧体岩石，就有可能发现玄武岩。玄武岩也可以通过其他<span class=\"name name-fuel\">高温</span>世界的地表金属和<span class=\"name name-earth\">磁化铁氧体</span>精炼获得。",
    "TraditionalChinese": "<span class=\"name name-earth\">玄武岩</span>主要可見於<span class=\"name name-fuel\">火山環境</span>的世界。常見於大型資源產地，並可用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析護目鏡</span>找到。<br><br>常見的鐵氧體岩石在使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析護目鏡</span>檢驗後可能會產出玄武岩。玄武岩可從<span class=\"name name-earth\">磁化鐵氧體</span>及來自其他<span class=\"name name-fuel\">高溫</span>世界的地形金屬精製而成。"
  },
  "PinObjectiveMessage": {
    "English": "Use the <span class=\"name name-technology\">Analysis Visor</span> to locate <span class=\"name name-earth\">Basalt</span> deposits<br>Basalt is found on worlds with <span class=\"name name-fuel\">volcanic environment</span>",
    "SimplifiedChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析面甲</span>定位<span class=\"name name-earth\">玄武岩</span>资源点<br>玄武岩存在于<span class=\"name name-fuel\">遍布火山</span>的星球上",
    "TraditionalChinese": "使用<span class=\"name name-technology\">分析護目鏡</span>找到<span class=\"name name-earth\">玄武岩</span>資源產地<br>玄武岩可見於<span class=\"name name-fuel\">火山環境</span>的世界"
